{"tid":1391140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"贊成獨立調查　盛智文：若無做錯警察毋須擔心","createTime":"2019-07-31T10:42:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T11:04:18.000Z","uid":51271,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"197537213601ef820a617e528a90c404f465e633","tid":1391140,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:42:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190731/s00001/1564559091031/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e8%b4%8a%e6%88%90%e7%8d%a8%e7%ab%8b%e8%aa%bf%e6%9f%a5-%e7%9b%9b%e6%99%ba%e6%96%87-%e8%8b%a5%e7%84%a1%e5%81%9a%e9%8c%af%e8%ad%a6%e5%af%9f%e6%af%8b%e9%a0%88%e6%93%94%e5%bf%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190731%2Fs00001%2F1564559091031%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e8%25b4%258a%25e6%2588%2590%25e7%258d%25a8%25e7%25ab%258b%25e8%25aa%25bf%25e6%259f%25a5-%25e7%259b%259b%25e6%2599%25ba%25e6%2596%2587-%25e8%258b%25a5%25e7%2584%25a1%25e5%2581%259a%25e9%258c%25af%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e5%25af%259f%25e6%25af%258b%25e9%25a0%2588%25e6%2593%2594%25e5%25bf%2583&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFjyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=95c5bfbb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190731%2Fs00001%2F1564559091031%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e8%25b4%258a%25e6%2588%2590%25e7%258d%25a8%25e7%25ab%258b%25e8%25aa%25bf%25e6%259f%25a5-%25e7%259b%259b%25e6%2599%25ba%25e6%2596%2587-%25e8%258b%25a5%25e7%2584%25a1%25e5%2581%259a%25e9%258c%25af%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e5%25af%259f%25e6%25af%258b%25e9%25a0%2588%25e6%2593%2594%25e5%25bf%2583&h=e524d116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190731/s00001/1564559091031/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e8%b4%8a%e6%88%90%e7%8d%a8%e7%ab%8b%e8%aa%bf%e6%9f%a5-%e7%9b%9b%e6%99%ba%e6%96%87-%e8%8b%a5%e7%84%a1%e5%81%9a%e9%8c%af%e8%ad%a6%e5%af%9f%e6%af%8b%e9%a0%88%e6%93%94%e5%bf%83</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反修訂《逃犯條例》觸發多場警民衝突，<strong>曾為特首林鄭月娥助選的蘭桂坊集團主席盛智文，今日（31日）出席活動後表示，贊成成立獨立調查委員會，調查整個反修例事件和各方責任，若警方本身沒做錯事，面對透明調查是毋須擔心，即使有警察犯錯，也不是整個警隊犯錯，而犯錯的人需要負責。</strong><br />\n<br />\n對於林鄭月娥始終拒絕「撤回」修例，他說不清楚背後原因，但認為「壽終正寢（dead）」的形容較撤回更強，相信任何理智的人都不會再提出修例。<br />\n<br />\n問及林鄭月娥是否須為修例風波下台，盛智文表示，目前看不到任何人可接任特首一職，若獨立調查發現林太須負責，她便應下台，惟目前為了社會穩定，林太應該留任。"},{"pid":"ed6aab02d56abf8036385b5efc45c8c3133e133d","tid":1391140,"uid":216789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:51:55.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"ac294e37bef0e7d388ac6a8d37bda192abd0a6b2","tid":1391140,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:54:24.000Z","msg":"佛地魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba4ffd50cf9577b9de0b012c758085206d229be9","tid":1391140,"uid":240251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:00:36.000Z","msg":"入黎講低你想<span style=\"color: gold;\">支持既黃商</span>／<span style=\"color: blue;\">抵制既藍商</span>！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b899fba1bfbd21aa45c9724e50cced50aa1f2e","tid":1391140,"uid":253826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:01:33.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n［請廣傳]大量文宣！大量文宣！大量文宣！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1390733\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1390733</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f252bef00ed